			Profile
			
			
Hung-hsinChenisanAssociateProfessorinMarketing&amp;Strategy,SchoolofManagement,ZhejiangUniversity.
HewasalsoatutortodoctoralstudentsinSchoolofManagementinSeptember2010.
HeisarecipientofZhejiangProvincialAwardforForeign-educatedElites(2011-2012).
HewasanAssistantProfessorinDepartmentofInternationalBusiness,YuanZeUniversity,Taiwan.

HereceivedhisPhDdegreefromManchesterBusinessSchoolin2003,MScdegreefromWarwickManufacturingCenterin1999,andBScdegreefromTaipeiMedicalUniversityPharmacySchoolin1995.
Hiscurrentresearchinterestsincludealliancestrategies,marketingstrategy,healthcaremarketing,andinternationalmanagement.
Hehasbeenthesisadvisorto4MBAstudents,22EMBAstudents,and2PhDstudentswhosuccessfullyreceivedtheirdegrees.

Hehaspublishedarticlesinseveralinternationaljournals,includingJournalofWorldBusiness(SSCI),ServiceIndustriesjournal(SSCI),JournalofBusinessResearch(SSCI),Telemedicineande-Health(SCI),andEuropeanBusinessReview(BHI).
Heisalsoanactivereviewerforseveralacademicjournals,includingTheServiceIndustriesJournal(SSCI)(2009,2010),TourismManagement(SSCI)(2010),AcademyofInternationalBusiness(AIB)AnnualConference(2005,2006,2007,2008,2009,2010),JournalofManagement&amp;Systems(2005,2006,2009),IndustryManagementReview(2009).

Dr.ChenwasheadpharmacistinaprestigioushospitalinTaipei.Healsoservedasanexecutiveadvisorinalargehealthcaregroup,andpharmaceuticalandmedicalsuppliescompanieslistedinTaipeiStockExchange.
HehasbeenprojectcoordinatorinmanyacademicandgovernmentalprojectsinTaiwan.
HehasalsobeenanexperiencedinterpreterofJointCommissionInternational(JCI)Accreditationforseveralhospitals,includingNationalTaiwanUniversityHospital,ChinaMedicalUniversityHospital,Min-ShengGeneralHospital,ChangBingShowChwanMemorialHospital.

Dr.ChenisaRescueDiverofProfessionalAssociationofDiverInstructor(PADI)certifiedinEngland.HealsoholdstheentrylevelcertificateofIkenobofloralart.


			
				
